---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Burn & Cedarwood — Rusty Notebooks">
<div class="chapter-bg" style="--bg-image: url('/images/burnandcedarwood.png');">
<div class="chapter-content">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="eyebrow">Chapter I — Burn & Cedarwood — Resonance of Rust</div>
    <h1>Burn & Cedarwood</h1>
    <p>
      Rusty wakes up before sunrise. The house is still, the road outside is empty,
      and for a moment everything feels suspended between staying and leaving.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Official Visualizer</h2>

    <div style="position:relative; padding-top:56.25%; border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:14px; overflow:hidden; background:#000;">
      <iframe
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/reBUbEqAsxs"
        title="Quiet Morning Official Visualizer"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
        allowfullscreen
        style="position:absolute; inset:0; width:100%; height:100%; border:0;"
      ></iframe>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>From Rusty’s notebook</h2>
    <p>
      I woke up before the sun again. The boards in the hallway still knew my steps.
      The coffee turned black in the cup before I touched it.
    </p>
    <p>
      Out by the road, nothing moved. But I could feel it coming —
      that old pull toward somewhere else.
    </p>
  </section>

<section class="section">
  <h2>Listen</h2>

  <div style="display:flex; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
    <a
      href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=reBUbEqAsxs"
      target="_blank"
      class="platform-button youtube"
    >
      <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M23.5 6.2a2.9 2.9 0 0 0-2-2C19.7 3.7 12 3.7 12 3.7s-7.7 0-9.5.5a2.9 2.9 0 0 0-2 2A30 30 0 0 0 0 12a30 30 0 0 0 .5 5.8 2.9 2.9 0 0 0 2 2c1.8.5 9.5.5 9.5.5s7.7 0 9.5-.5a2.9 2.9 0 0 0 2-2A30 30 0 0 0 24 12a30 30 0 0 0-.5-5.8zM9.7 15.5V8.5l6.3 3.5-6.3 3.5z"/>
      </svg>
      <span>YouTube</span>
    </a>

    <a
      href="https://open.spotify.com/intl-de/track/537jkf4rmG2Vg5fryfzUeu?si=26093fea66b54f07"
      target="_blank"
      class="platform-button spotify"
    >
      <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24"  aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M12 0a12 12 0 1 0 0 24A12 12 0 0 0 12 0zm5.5 17.3a.8.8 0 0 1-1.1.3c-3-1.8-6.7-2.2-11-.9a.8.8 0 1 1-.5-1.6c4.7-1.4 8.9-1 12.3 1 .4.2.5.7.3 1.2zm1.6-3.4a1 1 0 0 1-1.4.3c-3.5-2.1-8.9-2.7-13-1.2a1 1 0 1 1-.7-1.9c4.7-1.6 10.7-1 14.9 1.5a1 1 0 0 1 .2 1.3zm.2-3.6c-4.2-2.5-11.2-2.7-15.2-1.3a1.2 1.2 0 1 1-.8-2.3c4.6-1.6 12.3-1.3 17.1 1.6a1.2 1.2 0 0 1-1.1 2z"/>
      </svg>
      <span>Spotify</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

  <p style="margin-top:40px;">
    <a href="/chapters/chapter1">← Back to Chapter 1</a>
  </p>
    </div> <!-- chapter-content -->
</div> <!-- chapter-bg -->
</Layout>